name: KLM A330-203 [PH-AOM] Windy Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Hey everyone, here's a quick video from me today, featuring PH-AOM, "Piazza San Marco - Venezia" landing at Calgary International Airport on runway 17R in some pretty windy conditions. Apologies for the lousy camera work (again), and I hope you enjoy this brief shot of KLM.

I'd also like to specially dedicate this video to TheYottaTube. In case you haven't heard of him, he's a spotter from Amsterdam Schiphol with some awesome HD videos. Channel here: youtube.com/theyottatube

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
